CLASS snoddasmannen/galimulator/StarPath snoddasmannen/galimulator/StarPath
	FIELD xFudge xFudge F
	FIELD yFudge yFudge F
	METHOD a setFudge (F)V
		COMMENT Actual x/y fudge is random. The provided argument is plainly the maximum amplitude of the fudge.
		ARG 1 fudgeFactor
	METHOD a move (FF)V
		COMMENT Move the fudge by the given x/y coordinates.
		ARG 1 x
		ARG 2 y
	METHOD b getPosition (F)Lcom/badlogic/gdx/math/Vector2;
		ARG 1 angle
